a) Schematic illustration of the operando characterization method and Raman spectroscopy setup adopted in investigating Li3InCl6 samples (middle), the operando optical images of Li3InCl6 samples with different exposing time in air with 30% humidity (left), and the Raman spectra evolution of Li3InCl6 samples (right). Reproduced with permission.[

160

] Copyright 2020, American Chemical Society. b) Schematic illustration of the Al2O3 coated Li3InCl6 samples. c) Mass‐time curves and water absorption rate of Li3InCl6 and modified Li3InCl6 samples. Reproduced with permission.[

